urry friends with all kinds of different treatments. Let your imagination run wild and impress not only your fuzzy customers, but everyone around with a completely renewed, colourful and healthy look. Everyone deserves to be happy, groomed and in style!\n\nCuteness overload and fur everywhere guaranteed!\n\nFour adorable animals to play with (we will have more soon):\n* Tiger\n* Piggie\n* Oxy\n* Deerling\n\nFeel free to use our wonderful grooming tools:\n* Futuristic vacuum cleaner\n* Toothsie brushes\n* Unbearably cute collars\n* Badass glasses\n* Cool Camera to take pictures\n* Totally realistic color sprays\n* Advanced fly hitting lash\n* Mosquito repellents\n* and much more", "short_description": "Immerse yourself into the role of a pet groomer at a cute pet clinic. Help adorable, furry friends with all kinds of different treatments. Let your imagination run wild and impress not only your fuzzy customers, but everyone around with a completely renewed, colourful and healthy look. Everyone deserves to be happy, groomed and in style!\n\nCuteness overload and fur everywhere guaranteed!"}]}, "developer_name": "HyperVR Games", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://hypervr.games/privacy/petsnstuff.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "HyperVR Games", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://hypervr.games/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["